[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man suffers facial injuries in attack in Maryhill in Glasgow

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man is being treated in hospital for facial injuries after he was assaulted in the Maryhill area of Glasgow.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The attack happened on Shakespeare Street in the early hours of Monday morning.
A Police Scotland spokesman said officers were looking for two men in connection with the incident.
The injured man was said to be in a stable condition.
